				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've always assumed that most of the other classes' transformations are actual transformations, i.e., mystics change the person into an actual beaver, and not just an illusion.  Similarly with some of those elemental forms, either changing the person into an elemental, or coating them in fire/ice/whatever, a la The Human Torch.  I'm waiting to see the full spell list for illusions, but I don't think the other class spells are meant to be illusions.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
